he Eiffel Tower, equestrian at the Palace of Versailles, and urban sports at Place de la Concorde.\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 986, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.27002803555669e-18, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The surfing competition will take place nearly 10,000 miles from Paris in Tahiti, a part of French Polynesia.\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.634887803878333e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1082, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999987821866, \"rank\": 1.2173948918238997e-09, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCU will surround this unprecedented Olympic presentation with its most comprehensive coverage plan ever.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1119, \"end\": 1123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following are all the ways for U.S. viewers to watch the 2024 Paris Olympics:  OPENING CEREMONY  NBC DAYTIME  Fans can expect to see live coverage of the most exciting Olympic events, including the biggest stars, live finals, and medal events.\", \"f