\"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Cooper_(footballer)\"}, {\"begin\": 1771, \"end\": 1778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5204968560695345e-12, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheWatch with Alex Cooperinteractive program will feature Cooper and friends live in a seamless picture-in-picture view sharing their thoughts and insights on Olympic events and answering questions from fans on social in real time.\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 2012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1795, \"end\": 1799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9999982789564714, \"rank\": 1.7207505662616632e-06, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold Zone:The whip-around show will stream for the first time live on Peacock during NBCUniversal's coverage of the Olympic Games Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2099, \"end\": 2111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999998144631, \"rank\": 1.8518993400094266e-10, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With hostsScott Hanson,Andrew Siciliano,Matt IsemanandAkbar Gbajabiamila, Gold Zonewill stream live on Peacock from 7 a.m. - 5 p.m.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2172, \"end\": 2178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hanson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.678749047371973e-18, \"text\": \"Hanson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hanson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hanson\"}, {\"begin\": 2179, \"end\": 2195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Siciliano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Siciliano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Siciliano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Siciliano\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ET each day from July 27-Aug. 10.\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With up to 40 events happening simultaneously during the Paris Olympic Games,Gold Zonewill present viewers with the best and most compelling moments happening at any time.Gold Zone's daily offering will provide viewers with the most comprehensive and all-encompassing live whip-around coverage of any Olympic Games to date.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your Daily Olympic Recap on Peacock: Peacock is harnessing A.I.\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2707, \"end\": 2711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999992496669, \"rank\": 7.498795812092478e-10, \"text\": \"A.I.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"technology to present \\\"Your Daily Olympic Recap on Peacock,\\\" a first-of-its-kind, personalized experience complementing NBCUniversal's comprehensive coverage of the Olympic Games Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2832, \"end\": 2844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999998144631, \"rank\": 1.8518993400094266e-10, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In collaboration with Emmy Award-winning, Hall of Fame announcerAl Michaelsand powered by generative A.I.\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 3009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3005, \"end\": 3009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999992496669, \"rank\": 7.498795812092478e-10, \"text\": \"A.I.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"and A.I.\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3014, \"end\": 3018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999992496669, \"rank\": 7.498795812092478e-10, \"text\": \"A.I.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"voice synthesis technology, \\\"Your Daily Olympic Recap on Peacock\\\" will provide fans with their own customized playlist featuring highlights of the events most relevant to them from the previous day.\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Each compilation will feature clips from NBCU's Olympics coverage and be narrated by a high-quality A.I.\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3259, \"end\": 3263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 3318, \"end\": 3322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999992496669, \"rank\": 7.498795812092478e-10, \"text\": \"A.I.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"re-creation of Michaels' voice, which was trained using his past appearances on NBC and matches his signature expertise and elocution.\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3403, \"end\": 3406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9819888074021589, \"rank\": 0.018341531831068333, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CABLE NETWORKS  Paris Extra 1: A team sports-focused channel featuring events such as basketball, handball, water polo, field hockey, and more.\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3477, \"end\": 3482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.634887803878333e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"oParis Extra 2: A combat and racket sport-focused channel featuring events such as judo, taekwondo, badminton, table tennis, and more.\", \"from\": 3606, \"to\": 3740, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"oParis Extra 1andParis Extra 2will be available on Comcast, Cox, DirecTV/DirecTV Stream, Dish/Sling, Fubo, Hulu Live, Verizon, YouTube TV, and select participating NCTC members  SPANISH-LANGUAGE  AUTHENTICATED STREAMING  THEATER EXPERIENCES  IMAX: The NBC television network will extend its live coverage of the 2024 Paris Olympics Opening Ceremony to IMAX locations nationwide on Friday, July 26 - the first time ever the global event will be presented live in IMAX.\", \"from\": 3742, \"to\": 4209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3793, \"end\": 3800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"score\": 0.9999992866026148, \"rank\": 7.133978642768617e-07, \"text\": \"Comcast\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\"}, {\"begin\": 3836, \"end\": 3841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sling_TV\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.085562547021153e-12, \"text\": \"Sling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sling_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sling_TV\"}, {\"begin\": 3860, \"end\": 3867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Verizon_Fios\", \"score\": 0.9999999999481588, \"rank\": 5.2147686545338494e-11, \"text\": \"Verizon\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Verizon_Fios\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Verizon_Fios\"}, {\"begin\": 3869, \"end\": 3879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"YouTube TV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube_TV\"}, {\"begin\": 3906, \"end\": 3910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Counterterrorism_Center\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NCTC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Counterterrorism_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Counterterrorism_Center\"}, {\"begin\": 3994, \"end\": 3997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9819888074021589, \"rank\": 0.018341531831068333, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"IMAX will present NBC's live coverage of this summer's Opening Ceremony to more than 150 IMAX locations throughout the United States, providing fans with a unique and immersive theatre experience to enjoy what promises to be one of the most spectacular Opening Ceremonies in Olympic history.Tickets are available for purchase now.\", \"from\": 4211, \"to\": 4541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4229, \"end\": 4232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9819888074021589, \"rank\": 0.018341531831068333, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 4266, \"end\": 4282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999705377078608, \"rank\": 2.6952981168957952e-05, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}, {\"begin\": 4330, \"end\": 4343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999021329179, \"rank\": 9.782844661373095e-08, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AMC: The NBC television network will extend its daily live daytime coverage of the 2024 Paris Olympics to AMC Theatres as a ticketed event throughout the United States from July 27-August 11.\", \"from\": 4543, \"to\": 4734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4552, \"end\": 4555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9819888074021589, \"rank\": 0.018341531831068333, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 4649, \"end\": 4661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMC_Theatres\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AMC Theatres\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMC_Theatres\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMC_Theatres\"}, {\"begin\": 4697, \"end\": 4710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999021329179, \"rank\": 9.782844661373095e-08, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beginning the day after the Opening Ceremony, select daytime hours of NBCUniversal's live coverage of the 2024 Paris Olympics on NBC will be shown in approximately 160 AMC locations nationwide, allowing fans to gather and experience the competitions, moments, stories, and emotion of the Olympics on the big screen as they unfold live in Paris.Tickets are available for purchase now.\", \"from\": 4736, \"to\": 5119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4764, \"end\": 4780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999705377078608, \"rank\": 2.6952981168957952e-05, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}, {\"begin\": 4806, \"end\": 4818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999998144631, \"rank\": 1.8518993400094266e-10, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 4865, \"end\": 4868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9819888074021589, \"rank\": 0.018341531831068333, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 4904, \"end\": 4907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMC_Networks\", \"score\": 0.9999999943238436, \"rank\": 5.6758298677094855e-09, \"text\": \"AMC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMC_Networks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AMC_Networks\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ACCESSIBILITY  NBCUniversal's coverage of the Olympic Games Paris 2024 willbe more accessible to viewers of all abilities than ever before, providing the opportunity to enjoy the excitement of the Olympic through enhanced closed captioning, expanded audio description, and improved digital content accessibility.\", \"from\": 5121, \"to\": 5433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Closed captioning, which provides text of the coverage audio for viewers who are Deaf or hard of hearing, will be available for all Olympic events airing across NBCU's broadcast and cable networks.\", \"from\": 5435, \"to\": 5632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5596, \"end\": 5600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCUniversal will also provide closed captioning for all digital livestreams with commentary across Peacock, NBCSports.com and the NBC Sports app.\", \"from\": 5633, \"to\": 5779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5633, \"end\": 5645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999998144631, \"rank\": 1.8518993400094266e-10, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 5733, \"end\": 5740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5204968560695345e-12, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}, {\"begin\": 5742, \"end\": 5755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCSports.com\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 5764, \"end\": 5774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9988485024695387, \"rank\": 0.00115282391076879, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More audio description services - interspersing broadcast audio with skilled voices describing Olympic scenes and context - will be available for viewers who are blind or visually impaired for the Paris Olympics than any previous Games.\", \"from\": 5781, \"to\": 6017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All coverage on NBC, including daytime, primetime, and late night, and theGold Zonewhip-around showon Peacock will feature audio description, provided by Descriptive Video Works.\", \"from\": 6018, \"to\": 6196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6034, \"end\": 6037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9819888074021589, \"rank\": 0.018341531831068333, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a first for a U.S. broadcaster, audio description services for NBC coverage will be provided in stereo, enhancing the quality of sound for viewers.\", \"from\": 6197, \"to\": 6347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6263, \"end\": 6266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9819888074021589, \"rank\": 0.018341531831068333, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CONTENT CREATORS  AUDIO  iHeartMedia: NBCUniversal has chosen iHeartMedia as its exclusive audio partner for the Olympic Games Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 6349, \"to\": 6487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6387, \"end\": 6399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999998144631, \"rank\": 1.8518993400094266e-10, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As part of the agreement, iHeartRadio will provide 24/7 play-by-play audio channels of select NBCU linear coverage of the Games; create an original Olympic iHeartPodcast hosted byBowen YangandMatt Rogers; produce Olympic-specific episodes from some of iHeart's top podcasts; and promote tune-in for NBCU's comprehensive coverage.\", \"from\": 6488, \"to\": 6817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6582, \"end\": 6586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 6787, \"end\": 6791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The play-by-play channels will enable iHeart's listeners to hear NBCU's coverage of the most exciting moments of the Games, with a special focus on Team USA.\", \"from\": 6819, \"to\": 6976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6884, \"end\": 6888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 6967, \"end\": 6975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997477755739839, \"rank\": 0.0002522755083673205, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. has led the medal count at seven consecutive Summer Games and looks to be a powerhouse again.\", \"from\": 6977, \"to\": 7079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCU's coverage on iHeart's channels is expected to include Team USA men's and women's basketball, soccer, and volleyball, as well as swimming, gymnastics, track & field, and more.\", \"from\": 7080, \"to\": 7260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7080, \"end\": 7084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 7140, \"end\": 7148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997477755739839, \"rank\": 0.0002522755083673205, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the original podcast series, 2 Guys, 5 Rings: Matt, Bowen & the Olympics, Bowen Yang and Matt Rogersdiscuss everything from Paris culture to the athletes, events and top storylines of the 2024 Paris Olympic Games  My New Favorite Olympian:NBCUniversal Local's NBC-owned stations and NBC Sports Regional Networks present a new season of the award-winning multiplatform podcastMy New Favorite Olympianprofiling Team USA's most-inspiring athletes leading up to Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 7262, \"to\": 7734, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7339, \"end\": 7349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bowen_Yang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bowen Yang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bowen_Yang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bowen_Yang\"}, {\"begin\": 7389, \"end\": 7394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.634887803878333e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 7504, \"end\": 7516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999998144631, \"rank\": 1.8518993400094266e-10, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 7548, \"end\": 7576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports_Regional_Networks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.160959339342005e-50, \"text\": \"NBC Sports Regional Networks\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports_Regional_Networks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports_Regional_Networks\"}, {\"begin\": 7643, \"end\": 7655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Favorite\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"New Favorite\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Favorite\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Favorite\"}, {\"begin\": 7674, \"end\": 7682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997477755739839, \"rank\": 0.0002522755083673205, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 7723, \"end\": 7733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.73235227644746e-45, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The seven-part audio and video series, which began June 12, is led by 12-time Olympic medalist swimmerNatalie CoughlinandZena Keita, an NBC Sports Bay Area reporter, host and analyst.\", \"from\": 7735, \"to\": 7918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7871, \"end\": 7890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports_Bay_Area\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Sports Bay Area\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports_Bay_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports_Bay_Area\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My New Favorite Olympianprovides in-depth narratives profiling established and emerging American stars who have overcome adversity, broken barriers, and committed to helping others as they pursue Olympic or Paralympic glory.\", \"from\": 7920, \"to\": 8144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7923, \"end\": 7935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Favorite\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"New Favorite\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Favorite\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Favorite\"}, {\"begin\": 8008, \"end\": 8016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6320046521243712e-20, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each 15 to 20-minute episode focuses on different Olympic and Paralympic hopefuls and includes interviews with the athlete, experts, and those closest to them.\", \"from\": 8145, \"to\": 8304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WATCH PARTY  PEACOCK AND NBC ARE ENSURING FANS DON'T MISS A MOMENT OF THE HISTORIC PARIS OLYMPICS OPENING CEREMONY WITH A LIVESTREAM AT SAN DIEGO COMIC-CON  Set in Ancient Rome, the new Peacock Original seriesThose About to Dietakes audiences back to the origins of arena sports.\", \"from\": 8306, \"to\": 8585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8492, \"end\": 8508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peacock_(streaming_service)\", \"score\": 0.9999999936162567, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Peacock Original\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peacock_(streaming_service)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peacock_(streaming_service)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just as guests will have the opportunity to experience the thrill of a chariot race for themselves at Peacock's fan activation at San Diego Comic-Con, the 2024 Olympic Games will begin in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 8586, \"to\": 8788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8688, \"end\": 8695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5204968560695345e-12, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}, {\"begin\": 8720, \"end\": 8725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"score\": 0.938325215032559, \"rank\": 0.06572858107122168, \"text\": \"Diego\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\"}, {\"begin\": 8774, \"end\": 8779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.634887803878333e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 8781, \"end\": 8787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999996057077492, \"rank\": 3.8664972534607426e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To kick off this fortuitous moment and bridge live-action sports from the past with the present, Peacock and NBC will stunt the Opening Ceremony on Friday morning, July 26th with a public viewing using a 20x30 foot digital board to livestream Peacock's feed.\", \"from\": 8789, \"to\": 9047, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8886, \"end\": 8893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5204968560695345e-12, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}, {\"begin\": 8898, \"end\": 8901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9819888074021589, \"rank\": 0.018341531831068333, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 8917, \"end\": 8933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999705377078608, \"rank\": 2.6952981168957952e-05, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}, {\"begin\": 9032, \"end\": 9039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5204968560695345e-12, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The excitement will kick off with an Ancient Roman-dressed band playing Olympic-inspired fanfare tunes marching through the Gaslamp District.\", \"from\": 9048, \"to\": 9189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The band will arrive at Peacock's activationfootprint, in front of the \\\"Circus Maximus,\\\" just in time for the Ceremony to begin, drawing in passersby along the way.\", \"from\": 9190, \"to\": 9354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9214, \"end\": 9221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5204968560695345e-12, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The full duration of the Opening Ceremony will be live-streamed, from 10:30am PT - 3pm PT.\", \"from\": 9355, \"to\": 9445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9380, \"end\": 9396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999705377078608, \"rank\": 2.6952981168957952e-05, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WHEN: Friday, July 26, 10:30am - 3:00pm PT  WHERE: 170 Sixth Ave, San Diego, CA 92101    THE OLYMPICS ON XFINITY X1  NBC OLYMPIC ZONE ON ROKU  NBCUniversal owns the U.S. media rights to the Olympic Games through 2032, which are scheduled for Paris (2024), Milan Cortina (2026), Los Angeles (2028) and Brisbane (2032).\", \"from\": 9447, \"to\": 9764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9513, \"end\": 9522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Diego\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0534482319992268e-23, \"text\": \"San Diego\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Diego\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Diego\"}, {\"begin\": 9517, \"end\": 9522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"score\": 0.938325215032559, \"rank\": 0.06572858107122168, \"text\": \"Diego\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\"}, {\"begin\": 9689, \"end\": 9694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.634887803878333e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The host city for the 2030 Olympic Winter Games has not yet been chosen.\", \"from\": 9765, \"to\": 9837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"--PARIS OLYMPICS--  A Division ofNBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 9843, \"to\": 9889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9863, \"end\": 9873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999999108695, \"rank\": 8.925878716742796e-11, \"text\": \"A Division\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DISCLAIMER: This site and the products offered are for entertainment purposes only, and there is no gambling offered on this site.\", \"from\": 9891, \"to\": 10021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This service is intended for adult audiences.\", \"from\": 10022, \"to\": 10067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No guarantees are made for any specific outcome.\", \"from\": 10068, \"to\": 10116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, please call 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 10117, \"to\": 10194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u24b8 2024 NBC Universal\", \"from\": 10196, \"to\": 10216, \"entities\": []}]}"